tellraw @s[tag=swPool_EN] [{"text":"➇ ","color":"gold"},{"text":"If you are not in Creative mode, please keep your offhand slot empty during the game. Some arrows (invisible to others) will be given to you before each turn. Do not log out before your turn ends, or the arrows may not be given.\nBefore entering Practice mode, please keep your inventory as empty as possible, as many balls will be given to you."}]
tellraw @s[tag=swPool_CN] [{"text":"➇ ","color":"gold"},{"text":"如果不是创造模式，请在游戏过程中保持副手栏为空。每回合开始前会给予你一些箭（对其他玩家不可见）。请不要在回合结束前退出游戏，否则可能无法获得箭。\n进入练习模式前，请尽量清空背包，因为系统会给予玩家大量球。"}]
